EPS for Howard Hughes (HHC) Expected At $0.87, Petrus Trust Company Lta Upped By $1.43 Million Its Ebay (EBAY) Stake


					
						July 27, 2017 - By wolcottdaily


Petrus Trust Company Lta increased Ebay Inc (EBAY) stake by 18.66% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Petrus Trust Company Lta acquired 49,373 shares as Ebay Inc (EBAY)’s stock rose 0.21%. The Petrus Trust Company Lta holds 313,923 shares with $9.32 million value, up from 264,550 last quarter. Ebay Inc now has $39.48B valuation. The stock declined 0.40% or $0.15 reaching $36.89 on the news. About 1.77M shares traded. eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY) has risen 44.45% since July 27, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 27.75% the S&P500.







 Analysts expect Howard Hughes Corp (NYSE:HHC) to report $0.87 EPS on August, 7 after the close.They anticipate $0.71 EPS change or 44.94% from last quarter’s $1.58 EPS. HHC’s profit would be $35.08 million giving it 35.99 P/E if the $0.87 EPS is correct. After having $0.13 EPS previously, Howard Hughes Corp’s analysts see 569.23% EPS growth. About 6,642 shares traded. Howard Hughes Corp (NYSE:HHC) has risen 25.50% since July 27, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 8.80% the S&P500.
Investors sentiment increased to 0.97 in 2016 Q4. Its up 0.22, from 0.75 in 2016Q3. It increased, as 77 investors sold EBAY shares while 258 reduced holdings. 88 funds opened positions while 236 raised stakes. 889.22 million shares or 2.82% less from 915.05 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Keybank National Association Oh invested in 26,310 shares. Stifel Financial Corporation holds 0.13% or 1.04M shares in its portfolio. Teachers Retirement Sys Of The State Of Kentucky holds 128,500 shares. Pillar Pacific Mgmt Ltd Liability Corporation invested 0.28% in eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY). Cibc Ww holds 0.08% or 276,570 shares. Gabelli Funds Ltd Co stated it has 393,000 shares or 0.07% of all its holdings. Synovus Corporation holds 21,936 shares. Paloma Prns Mgmt holds 81,788 shares or 0.02% of its portfolio. Sumitomo Mitsui Asset Management Ltd owns 79,929 shares or 0.05% of their US portfolio. Hsbc Public Limited Co owns 1.27 million shares or 0.09% of their US portfolio. Macquarie Grp Ltd owns 6.69 million shares. Thematic Prtn Lc, New York-based fund reported 3.06M shares. Weiss Multi holds 80,331 shares or 0.12% of its portfolio. Whittier holds 0.01% of its portfolio in eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY) for 8,436 shares. Moreover, Great Lakes Advsrs Ltd Limited Liability Company has 0.02% invested in eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY).
Since January 30, 2017, it had 0 insider purchases, and 18 insider sales for $16.24 million activity. 2,903 shares valued at $99,030 were sold by Doerger Brian J. on Friday, May 12. TIERNEY THOMAS J sold $200,157 worth of eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY) on Wednesday, February 8. 6,204 eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY) shares with value of $213,236 were sold by Lee Jae Hyun. FISHER STEPHEN sold $560,621 worth of stock or 16,601 shares. $402,568 worth of eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY) shares were sold by Mitic Kathleen C.. PITTMAN RAYMOND J sold 35,000 shares worth $1.20M. The insider Lawton III Harry A sold 13,400 shares worth $451,922.
Among 38 analysts covering eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY), 20 have Buy rating, 2 Sell and 16 Hold. Therefore 53% are positive. eBay Inc had 102 analyst reports since July 21, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. The company was downgraded on Thursday, August 27 by Vetr. The firm has “Buy” rating given on Thursday, July 21 by Axiom Capital. Hilliard Lyons initiated it with “Long-Term Buy” rating and $35 target in Tuesday, August 30 report. Robert W. Baird maintained the shares of EBAY in report on Thursday, July 13 with “Buy” rating. The firm has “Strong Buy” rating by Jyske Bank given on Wednesday, January 13. As per Monday, October 17, the company rating was maintained by Benchmark. The rating was maintained by Benchmark with “Buy” on Thursday, July 21. The stock of eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY) has “Buy” rating given on Thursday, June 23 by Maxim Group. The stock has “Underweight” rating by Morgan Stanley on Tuesday, April 19. On Thursday, July 21 the stock rating was maintained by RBC Capital Markets with “Sector Perform”.
Among 7 analysts covering Howard Hughes (NYSE:HHC), 5 have Buy rating, 1 Sell and 1 Hold. Therefore 71% are positive. Howard Hughes had 11 analyst reports since August 14, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. The stock has “Buy” rating by Citigroup on Friday, May 13. Sandler O’Neill initiated Howard Hughes Corp (NYSE:HHC) rating on Thursday, March 30. Sandler O’Neill has “Hold” rating and $123 target. The stock of Howard Hughes Corp (NYSE:HHC) has “Sell” rating given on Thursday, September 24 by TheStreet. The firm earned “Market Outperform” rating on Monday, October 31 by CJS Securities. Citigroup maintained Howard Hughes Corp (NYSE:HHC) on Wednesday, August 10 with “Buy” rating. Compass Point maintained Howard Hughes Corp (NYSE:HHC) on Tuesday, December 8 with “Buy” rating. The rating was maintained by JMP Securities on Sunday, August 16 with “Buy”. The rating was initiated by BWS Financial with “Buy” on Thursday, June 8. Compass Point maintained the shares of HHC in report on Monday, May 23 with “Buy” rating.
Investors sentiment decreased to 1.26 in Q4 2016. Its down 0.10, from 1.36 in 2016Q3. It fall, as 16 investors sold Howard Hughes Corp shares while 62 reduced holdings. 24 funds opened positions while 74 raised stakes. 31.22 million shares or 1.07% more from 30.89 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Massmutual Trust Com Fsb Adv holds 100 shares. Swift Run Capital Llc accumulated 3.99% or 59,293 shares. Baillie Gifford And, a United Kingdom-based fund reported 1.75 million shares. Glenmede Tru Na accumulated 0% or 117 shares. Paloma Prtnrs stated it has 8,893 shares. New South Management Inc owns 998,688 shares or 2.72% of their US portfolio. Mitsubishi Ufj Banking invested 0.02% in Howard Hughes Corp (NYSE:HHC). Lederer Associate Invest Counsel Ca has 11,400 shares. Blackrock Gru invested 0% in Howard Hughes Corp (NYSE:HHC). Voya Invest Management Lc reported 11,394 shares or 0% of all its holdings. Knightsbridge Asset Mngmt Ltd Liability invested in 6,422 shares or 0.68% of the stock. Rhumbline Advisers has invested 0.01% in Howard Hughes Corp (NYSE:HHC). California Employees Retirement Systems invested in 78,300 shares. Fortress Inv Grp Inc Ltd owns 3,081 shares. Northwestern Mutual Wealth Management Com holds 120 shares.
Since March 8, 2017, it had 0 insider purchases, and 3 selling transactions for $10.13 million activity. 30,000 shares were sold by Curry Christopher John, worth $3.80M on Monday, June 5. The insider Davidsohn Reuben Seth sold 5,981 shares worth $710,423.








