on BusinessWire - BZX











Howard Hughes Corp.


            
            The Howard Hughes Corp. engages in the development of master planned communities (MPC) and mixed-used properties. It operates through the following segments: MPC, Operating Assets, and Strategic Developments. The MPC segment consists of the development and sale of residential and commercial land, primarily in large-scale projects. The Operating Assets segment consists of properties, investments, and other assets, such as retail, office, multi-family, and hospitality properties. The Strategic Developments segment comprises of other real estate assets in the form of entitled and unentitled land and residential condominium developments. The company was founded on November 9, 2010 and is headquartered in Dallas, TX.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  




