EPS for Howard Hughes (HHC) Expected At $0.87, Petrus Trust Company Lta Upped By $1.43 Million Its Ebay (EBAY) Stake


					
						July 27, 2017 - By wolcottdaily


Petrus Trust Company Lta increased Ebay Inc (EBAY) stake by 18.66% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Petrus Trust Company Lta acquired 49,373 shares as Ebay Inc (EBAY)’s stock rose 0.21%. The Petrus Trust Company Lta holds 313,923 shares with $9.32 million value, up from 264,550 last quarter. Ebay Inc now has $39.48B valuation. The stock declined 0.40% or $0.15 reaching $36.89 on the news. About 1.77M shares traded. eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY) has risen 44.45% since July 27, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 27.75% the S&P500.







 Analysts expect Howard Hughes Corp (NYSE:HHC) to report $0.87 EPS on August, 7 after the close.They anticipate $0.71 EPS change or 44.94% from last quarter’s $1.58 EPS. HHC’s profit would be $35.08 million giving it 35.99 P/E if the $0.87 EPS is correct. After having $0.13 EPS previously, Howard Hughes Corp’s analysts see 569.23% EPS growth. About 6,642 shares traded. Howard Hughes Corp (NYSE:HHC) has risen 25.50% since July 27, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 8.80% the S&P500.
Investors sentiment increased to 0.97 in 2016 Q4. Its up 0.22, from 0.75 in 2016Q3. It increased, as 77 investors sold EBAY shares while 258 reduced holdings. 88 funds opened positions while 236 raised stakes. 889.22 million shares or 2.82% less from 915.05 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Keybank National Association Oh invested in 26,310 shares. Stifel Financial Corporation holds 0.13% or 1.04M shares in its portfolio. Teachers Retirement Sys Of The State Of Kentucky holds 128,500 shares. Pillar Pacific Mgmt Ltd Liability Corporation invested 0.28% in eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY). Cibc Ww holds 0.08% or 276,570 shares. Gabelli Funds Ltd Co stated it has 393,000 shares or 0.07% of all its holdings. Synovus Corporation holds 21,936 shares. Paloma Prns Mgmt holds 81,788 shares or 0.02% of its portfolio. Sumitomo Mitsui Asset Management Ltd owns 79,929 shares or 0.05% of their US portfolio. Hsbc Public Limited Co owns 1.27 million shares or 0.09% of their US portfolio. Macquarie Grp Ltd owns 6.69 million shares. Thematic Prtn Lc, New York-based fund reported 3.06M shares. Weiss Multi holds 80,331 shares or 0.12% of its portfolio. Whittier holds 0.01% of its portfolio in eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY) for 8,436 shares. Moreover, Great Lakes Advsrs Ltd Limited Liability Company has 0.02% invested in eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY).
Since January 30, 2017, it had 0 insider purchases, and 18 insider sales for $16.24 million activity. 2,903 shares valued at $99,030 were sold by Doerger Brian J. on Friday, May 12. TIERNEY THOMAS J sold $200,157 worth of eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY) on Wednesday, February 8. 6,204 eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY) shares with value of $213,236 were sold by Lee Jae Hyun. FISHER STEPHEN sold $560,621 worth of stock or 16,601 shares. $402,568 worth of eBay Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY) shares were sold by Mitic Kathleen C.. PITTMAN RAYMOND J sold 35,000 shares worth $1.20M. The insider Lawton III Harry A sold 13,400 shares worth $451,922.
